                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-100-off580 t18080914-100-cd581"></join> was servant to <rs id="t18080914-100-viclabel582" type="occupation">sir</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-100-victim873 t18080914-100-viclabel582"></join> 
                  
                     
